# The repo stores LF; check out LF everywhere so the formatter sees the same
# bytes on Windows, in CI, and in the Docker build (core.autocrlf otherwise
# hands Biome CRLF locally and LF on Linux).
* text=auto eol=lf

*.ttf binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.ico binary

pnpm-lock.yaml linguist-generated=true -diff
